<i>big mystery or something.</i>

10
00:00:49,166 --> 00:00:50,916
<i>Which, it turns out...</i>

11
00:00:51,708 --> 00:00:53,375
<i>I guess it kind of was.</i>

12
00:01:00,208 --> 00:01:02,708
<i>So I should
start at the beginning,</i>

