Right. Sorry. I'm mourning.

30
00:01:49,791 --> 00:01:50,875
I'm mourning.

31
00:01:50,958 --> 00:01:53,541
<i>And number four: she mandated that I still go</i>

32
00:01:53,625 --> 00:01:56,208
